{"tid":2003021,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[另類] [滅共預言] 中共係咪爆左條龍脈23 之 地震鳥?","createTime":"2020-05-05T13:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T04:08:08.000Z","uid":140041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b719f5dd1b9005b7f23b518cd3e1dddd890dac32","tid":2003021,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"本討論不轉貼現代占星/網絡節目人仕預言<br />\n(因資料量大及凖確度不詳也尊重原創人仕之出處)<br />\n(古人已死另計)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">若各位自行轉貼請簡略及提供原出處</span><br />\n也請大家冷静思考，以免當局者迷<br />\n<br />\n本Post資料全沒科學根據，覺得岩睇睇落去，唔岩請回上一頁<br />\n舊帖重溫 (1-22) 請自行seach &quot;中共係咪爆左條龍脈XX&quot;<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於前post開始岀現物資及購買討論<br />\n以免過快爆Post物資討論及購買請移玉步至以下繼續<br />\n以作分流ㄧ&quot;常備有老佬箱/災難背囊&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1849767/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1849767/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">免責聲明 : 預言涉及風險，末日/混亂時期物資價格有時會大幅波動，價格可升亦可跌，胡亂購買更可變得毫無價值。 在作出成為末日能決定前，應仔細考慮物資 / 空間是否適合其財務狀況、目標和經驗、風險承受能力、以及其他有關情況，亦應了解投資物資所涉及的相關風險。 購買物資未必一定能夠安全，反而可能會招致損失。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本帖宗旨：<br />\n預言，係前人／古人／術士／特異之人推算將來嘅事<br />\n即係代表命中注定<br />\n無論大家做啲乜都影響唔到個結果<br />\n只係需要信同埋等待<br />\n不需要犯法行為<br />\n念力滅共、集體意志<br />\n天作孽猶可違，自作孽不可活<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-yzgoj/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/1518172/4117252/GBEFP2961__15740.1541823019.jpg?c=2&amp;imbypass=on\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn11.bigcommerce.com%2Fs-yzgoj%2Fimages%2Fstencil%2F1280x1280%2Fproducts%2F1518172%2F4117252%2FGBEFP2961__15740.1541823019.jpg%3Fc%3D2%26imbypass%3Don&h=d6345d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世上有人行大善，遭了此劫不上算<br />\n若得過了大劫年，才算世間不老仙<br />\n任你金剛鐵羅漢，除非善乃能保全[/member]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"914f01bc26e6b18cce205a4d44f34e7c2d0bd4c3","tid":2003021,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fdbf68ffc66420b70bf0c574683d0724070d88f","tid":2003021,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位使用不推文回覆，謝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入小圈子討論硏究中外預言及發掘新聞佐證<br />\n本post位處神秘台<br />\n難免有時大家講講下越講越遠<br />\n離題太遠要詳細專業討論如軍事/政制發展/未來願境規劃<br />\n請各位自律及自行另開新post討論<br />\n各方人仕也可互相提點<br />\n多謝合作<br />\n<br />\n此學術硏究預言Post針對大中華<br />\n如其他外國預言家並不是有詳細大中華預言<br />\n請另開新Post討論<br />\n<br />\n另外本討論/硏究根本上並不會有確實結論<br />\n理應不存在爭拗<br />\n如別有用心人仕引戰/引人離題<br />\n請各位自行分析有心人給引戰<br />\n不用浪費回覆/網上資源/心情及免過快爆Post"},{"pid":"d64b27f713b0810cdcadaaf203fb55340906f7d4","tid":2003021,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ac3de5f2004677b4988925ecc2c62bd449e73a","tid":2003021,"uid":254872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f197e5fd8421123b9cd7450de72eee10eb416f7c","tid":2003021,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次個POST5日玩爆左"},{"pid":"8c9978e91a4785b97b645646916f64d86d88c091","tid":2003021,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03d6248dcf58de4e5ac8f2fca5d9ce492db5df","tid":2003021,"uid":140041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"